high_descs: Turn left, walk down the passage and turn right to enter the room to reach the brown shelf.
Pick the gloves from the bottom shelf.
Put the gloves on the shelf above.
anns.task_desc: Put the gloves in the shelf above.

high_descs: Turn to your left, move straight, then turn to your right, move straight, again turn to your left facing the wooden shelf
Pick up the grey hand statue from the left bottom rack in the shelf
Put the grey hand statue on the rack above the left bottom rack in the shelf
anns.task_desc: Place the grey hand statue on the wooden shelf

high_descs: Turn to the left and move down the corridor. When you get to the door, turn left and enter the room and  turn left in front of the shelf.
Pick up the plastic hand that is at the bottom of the shelf
Move the plastic hand to the next shelf floor.
anns.task_desc: Move a plastic hand to one shelf floor to the next.

high_descs: Turn around and Walk towards to the statue and turn right and enter the statue.
Take the gloves from the statue.
Place the statue on the shelf rack.
anns.task_desc: Place the gloves on the Shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, walk down the corridor, take the distant exit to the right, and go to the statue in the upper left corner.
Pick up the statue from under the table that is next to the shelves.
Place the statue on the middle left shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the statue on the middle left shelf.
